[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Flask/itsdangerous Signing Mechanism                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Cookie Creation:**                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. JSON serialize session data: `{"user_id": "10032"}`                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Compact JSON format: `{"user_id":"10032"}`                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Base64 URL-safe encode: `eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoiMTAwMzIifQ`                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Generate timestamp/nonce: `aVd0oA`                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Compute HMAC-SHA1: `hmac_sha1(payload.timestamp, SECRET_KEY)`             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 6. Base64 URL-safe encode signature: `VqPUgS4MLdLZbrF9JRNetU8FfwI`           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 7. Format: `payload.timestamp.signature`                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Verification Process:**                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Split cookie into three parts                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Check timestamp expiration                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Recompute HMAC-SHA1(payload.timestamp, SECRET_KEY)                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Compare with received signature (constant-time comparison)                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Accept if match, reject (raise BadSignature) if mismatch                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
