[32m│[0m 7. ⚠️ **Protection depends ENTIRELY on SECRET_KEY secrecy**                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 8. ⚠️ **Leaked SECRET_KEY = Can forge sessions for ANY user**                 [32m│[0m
