[32m│[0m ## Why IDOR via Session Cookie Manipulation Fails                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The application appears to be using Flask's built-in session management with [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m cryptographic signatures. This means:                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
