[32m│[0m Based on my analysis of the application authentication flow, I have          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m important findings about the session handling:                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## Session Cookie Analysis                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Actual Results:                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Login POST Response:**                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
